---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { useTranslations } from '../../utils/i18n';

const locale = 'tr';
const t = useTranslations(locale);
---

<BaseLayout title="SSS - Ionyx Framework" description="Ionyx hakkında sıkça sorulan sorular">
	<section class="py-20 hero-gradient">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
				<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
					Sıkça Sorulan <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-ionyx-neon-purple to-ionyx-neon-blue bg-clip-text text-transparent">Sorular</span>
				</h1>
				<p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
					Ionyx hakkında merak edilenler
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-20">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<div class="space-y-6">
					<!-- Framework Comparison -->
					<div class="glass-dark rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
						<button class="w-full p-6 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('expanded')">
							<div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
								<div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-ionyx-neon-purple to-ionyx-neon-blue rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
									<span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">F</span>
								</div>
								<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Diğer framework'lerden farkı nedir?</h3>
							</div>
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
							</svg>
						</button>
						<div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
							<p class="mb-4">
								<strong class="text-white">Ionyx, minimalist desktop uygulama geliştirme için tasarlandı.</strong> 
								Electron, Tauri™ ve diğer framework'ler harika seçeneklerdir, ancak Ionyx farklı bir yaklaşım sunar:
							</p>
							<div class="bg-dark-tertiary rounded-lg p-4 border border-dark-border mb-4">
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-2">🎯 <strong class="text-white">Electron:</strong> Full-featured, Node.js tabanlı</p>
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-2">🎯 <strong class="text-white">Tauri™:</strong> Rust tabanlı, geniş ekosistem</p>
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-400">🎯 <strong class="text-white">Ionyx:</strong> Minimalist, ultra-küçük binary</p>
							</div>
							<p class="mb-4">
								Ionyx, sadece en temel özelliklere odaklanarak sub-3MB runtime hedefler. 
								Bu, onu küçük ve hızlı uygulamalar için ideal kılar.
							</p>
							<p class="text-xs text-gray-500">
								TAURI is a trademark of The Tauri Programme within the Commons Conservancy.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Binary Size -->
					<div class="glass-dark rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
						<button class="w-full p-6 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('expanded')">
							<div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
								<div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-ionyx-neon-purple to-ionyx-neon-blue rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
									<span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">B</span>
								</div>
								<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">1.66MB binary boyutu nasıl mümkün?</h3>
							</div>
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
							</svg>
						</button>
						<div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
							<p class="mb-4">
								Minimalist mühendislik prensipleri sayesinde:
							</p>
							<ul class="space-y-2 mb-4">
								<li class="flex items-start">
									<span class="text-green-400 mr-2">•</span>
									<span>Hiçbir gereksiz dependency yok</span>
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-start">
									<span class="text-green-400 mr-2">•</span>
									<span>Sadece en temel WRY (0.54.2) ve TAO (0.34.5) kütüphaneleri</span>
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-start">
									<span class="text-green-400 mr-2">•</span>
									<span>Ekstra runtime taşımıyoruz (sistem WebView kullanıyoruz)</span>
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-start">
									<span class="text-green-400 mr-2">•</span>
									<span>Optimize edilmiş Rust kodu</span>
								</li>
							</ul>
							<div class="bg-dark-tertiary rounded-lg p-4 border border-dark-border">
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
									<strong class="text-white">Breakdown:</strong> WRY (0.54.2) + TAO (0.34.5) + Ionyx Core (~0.8MB) = 1.66MB
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Frontend Framework -->
					<div class="glass-dark rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
						<button class="w-full p-6 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('expanded')">
							<div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
								<div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-ionyx-neon-purple to-ionyx-neon-blue rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
									<span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">F</span>
								</div>
								<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Hangi frontend framework'lerini destekliyor?</h3>
							</div>
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
							</svg>
						</button>
						<div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
							<p class="mb-4">
								<strong class="text-white">Ionyx frontend-agnostiktir.</strong> 
								Herhangi bir frontend framework ile çalışabilir:
							</p>
							<ul class="space-y-2 mb-4">
								<li class="flex items-start">
									<span class="text-green-400 mr-2">•</span>
									<span>React + TypeScript</span>
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-start">
									<span class="text-green-400 mr-2">•</span>
									<span>Vue.js + TypeScript</span>
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-start">
									<span class="text-green-400 mr-2">•</span>
									<span>Svelte + TypeScript</span>
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-start">
									<span class="text-green-400 mr-2">•</span>
									<span>Vanilla JavaScript</span>
								</li>
							</ul>
							<div class="bg-dark-tertiary rounded-lg p-4 border border-dark-border">
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
									<strong class="text-white">Not:</strong> Ionyx sadece backend'i sağlar, frontend tamamen size aittir.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Performance -->
					<div class="glass-dark rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
						<button class="w-full p-6 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('expanded')">
							<div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
								<div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-ionyx-neon-purple to-ionyx-neon-blue rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
									<span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">P</span>
								</div>
								<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Performans avantajları neler?</h3>
							</div>
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
							</svg>
						</button>
						<div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
							<p class="mb-4">
								<strong class="text-white">Ionyx'in performans avantajları:</strong>
							</p>
							<ul class="space-y-2 mb-4">
								<li class="flex items-start">
									<span class="text-green-400 mr-2">•</span>
									<span>&lt;30ms uygulama başlangıç süresi</span>
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-start">
									<span class="text-green-400 mr-2">•</span>
									<span>10-20MB memory kullanımı</span>
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-start">
									<span class="text-green-400 mr-2">•</span>
									<span>Minimal CPU kullanımı</span>
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-start">
									<span class="text-green-400 mr-2">•</span>
									<span>Sistem WebView ile native performans</span>
								</li>
							</ul>
							<div class="bg-dark-tertiary rounded-lg p-4 border border-dark-border">
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
									<strong class="text-white">Karşılaştırma:</strong> Electron (100-200MB) vs Ionyx (10-20MB)
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Production Ready -->
					<div class="glass-dark rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
						<button class="w-full p-6 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('expanded')">
							<div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
								<div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-ionyx-neon-purple to-ionyx-neon-blue rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
									<span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">P</span>
								</div>
								<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Production ready mı?</h3>
							</div>
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
							</svg>
						</button>
						<div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
							<p class="mb-4">
								<strong class="text-white">Ionyx şu anda geliştirme aşamasındadır.</strong>
							</p>
							<ul class="space-y-2 mb-4">
								<li class="flex items-start">
									<span class="text-yellow-400 mr-2">•</span>
									<span>Core API'ler geliştiriliyor</span>
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-start">
									<span class="text-yellow-400 mr-2">•</span>
									<span>CLI araçları üzerinde çalışılıyor</span>
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-start">
									<span class="text-yellow-400 mr-2">•</span>
									<span>Dokümantasyon genişletiliyor</span>
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-start">
									<span class="text-green-400 mr-2">•</span>
									<span>Topluluk katkılarına açıktır</span>
								</li>
							</ul>
							<div class="bg-dark-tertiary rounded-lg p-4 border border-dark-border">
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
									<strong class="text-white">Durum:</strong> Alpha sürümünde, production için hazır değil
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Learning Curve -->
					<div class="glass-dark rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
						<button class="w-full p-6 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('expanded')">
							<div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
								<div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-ionyx-neon-purple to-ionyx-neon-blue rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
									<span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">L</span>
								</div>
								<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Öğrenme eğrisi nasıl?</h3>
							</div>
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
							</svg>
						</button>
						<div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
							<p class="mb-4">
								<strong class="text-white">Ionyx öğrenmesi kolaydır:</strong>
							</p>
							<ul class="space-y-2 mb-4">
								<li class="flex items-start">
									<span class="text-green-400 mr-2">•</span>
									<span>Basit CLI komutları</span>
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-start">
									<span class="text-green-400 mr-2">•</span>
									<span>Standart web teknolojileri</span>
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-start">
									<span class="text-green-400 mr-2">•</span>
									<span>Az sayıda konsept</span>
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-start">
									<span class="text-green-400 mr-2">•</span>
									<span>Kapsamlı dokümantasyon</span>
								</li>
							</ul>
							<div class="bg-dark-tertiary rounded-lg p-4 border border-dark-border">
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
									<strong class="text-white">Gereksinimler:</strong> HTML/CSS/JS ve temel Rust bilgisi yeterli
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- CTA Section -->
				<div class="mt-16 text-center">
					<div class="glass p-8 rounded-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto">
						<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
							Daha fazla soru mu?
						</h2>
						<p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
							Topluluğumuza katılın veya GitHub'da tartışın.
						</p>
						<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-4">
							<a href="https://github.com/ionyx-apps/ionyx/discussions" class="btn-primary w-full sm:w-auto">
								GitHub Discussions
							</a>
							<a href="https://discord.gg/ionyx" class="btn-secondary w-full sm:w-auto">
								Discord
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.glass-dark.expanded .px-6.pb-6 {
		display: block;
	}
	
	.glass-dark:not(.expanded) .px-6.pb-6 {
		display: none;
	}
</style>
